f=Brand Studio/atlas/operational/skill/atlas-skill-routing.md · p=Atlas's routing map. Triggers: `operational/commands/atlas-commands.md`. · h2:Where Identity Fits=Atlas identity spark (Creative Director) holds Brand Studio's. Universal-only principles. · h2:The Lifecycle=`brand-identity          (CREATE — new business, no identity yet: 5-element system) \· \|                  output populates ↓ \· brand-guidelines        (ENFORCE — audit every asset vs the brand-kit file: PASS / fix list) \· + \· multi-brand-system      (SEPARATE — multi-venture operators only: distance + shared-set` · h2:The Lifecycle=Atlas's four skills cover brand's visual life order: · h2:Handoff Rules=**brand-identity brand-guidelines**: creation output fills `assets/brand-kit-template.md`; kit law brand-identity re-run redesigns (operator sign-off identity changes post-rollout cost 10×)., **brand-guidelines multi-brand-system**: multi-brand audits run own-kit compliance sibling-territory separation. BLEED findings repeat-violation drift notes route **spark**., **layout-composition brand-guidelines**: kit legislates spacing/clear-space; composition craft beyond (focal points, hierarchy levels, grid choice) layout-composition's. audit never fails asset unlegislated craft *recommend* layout-composition., **brand-identity multi-brand-system**: creating sibling brand consumes separation matrix constraint extends (operator approves new row). · h2:Cross-Agent Boundaries=**lena** owns words (content, tone, voice guides); atlas checks text *set* kit. brand-identity's voice sections defer lena's voice-guide files., **pixel** calls brand-guidelines inside asset-pipeline step pixel produces, atlas judges., **spark** consumes atlas's kit one three gate references, plus atlas's drift notes BLEED findings. Spark judges drift; operator amends kits/matrix., **Behavioral Science (when built)**: visual attention/salience findings (kahneman) inform kit rules operator-approved kit amendments, never hoc. · h2:Precedence="Is brand" brand-guidelines multi-brand-system brands). "Make/design our brand" brand-identity. "Lay out feel off" layout-composition. Ambiguous ask whether need create, audit, separate, compose. · f=kit request audit brand-guidelines' Phase-1 stop (offer template brand-identity). Anything else unclear ask.